---
description: Defines correct token usage per UI context (tables, sidebar, cards, buttons, overlays).
globs:
  - "src/components/**/*.vue"
alwaysApply: true
---

# UI Context Color Usage

Page layout → `bg-background text-foreground`  
Cards → `bg-card text-card-foreground`  
Descriptions → `text-muted-foreground`  
Table header → `bg-muted text-foreground`  
Primary button → `bg-primary text-primary-foreground`  
Destructive → `variant="destructive"`  
Sidebar → always `bg-sidebar` tokens  
Modal overlay → `bg-black/80` allowed  

Contrast must always follow semantic foreground pairing.